overview:
Gemrush is an online writer, a blogger and a tutor.

A few years ago, I was looking for an extra income when I happened upon a site that introduced writing as a way to earn money online. It was like a miracle that suddenly dropped on my feet. I busied myself ASAP because I knew that should I wait for a day, millions of people would be ahead of me. This started my career as a writer and blogger online.

Today I am discovering more ways of earning an income online. I am still learning a lot as I work on my computer.
